[COMPILING]:
            For compiling use Makefile:
            make

[RUN]:
      ./dtraffic [interface] [mode]
      [interface] = wlan0/eth0/ppp0 ec..
      [mode] = down/up

[EXAMPLE]:
          ./dtraffic wlan0 down


[NOTE]:
        This version in not completed.
